						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">King: Rājarāja I Year 11: 986 A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>Incomplete. Impression not available for this record. Records that the <hi rend="italic">ūrār</hi> of Kāṭṭūr in Paiyyūr-kōṭṭam sold two pieces of land, called Villipāgi Dāmōdara at Iraṅgaṇūr-kūvam, a <hi rend="italic">taṉkūṟu</hi> of Maṇaiyir-kōṭṭam. It is also recorded that the land was also freed from taxes.</p>						

